last_emails.subject: Welcome to Nomic Atlas
last_emails.body:
At Nomic, we're on a mission to make AI systems more accessible and explainable. AI systems are powered by and generate massive
amounts of unstructured data signals such as text, PDFs, images, audio, and embeddings. We believe the best way to leverage and
improve these systems is to look at the data that powers.
 
Welcome to Atlas, the world's best platform to operationalize your massive text, PDF, image, and embedding datasets.
 
Let's get you onboarded. Before you dive in, remember to join the Nomic Community Slack
[https://join.slack.com/t/nomic-community/shared_invite/zt-32yciio0n-XTQTOvDu~xXeDEqsNPnGUQ] for help with onboarding.


Getting your data into Atlas

Underpinning Atlas is an advanced AI-native data layer [https://atlas.nomic.ai/roles/ai-and-data-leaders]. Let's start by syncing
your data into Atlas.
